targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeInterval(updated_at) as "time",
  ${group_by},
  COUNT(*) AS executions
FROM "buildbuddy_prod"."ExecutionsView"
WHERE true
  AND group_id LIKE '${group_id}'
  AND updated_at_usec BETWEEN toUnixTimestamp64Micro($__fromTime_ms) AND toUnixTimestamp64Micro($__toTime_ms)
  AND effective_isolation_type LIKE '${effective_isolation_type}'
  AND action_mnemonic LIKE '${action_mnemonic}'
  AND region LIKE '${region}'
  AND self_hosted = ${self_hosted}
  AND ${other_filters}
GROUP by time, ${group_by}
ORDER BY time
